"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"12月13日消息，韩国大财阀SK集团旗下的投资子公司SK Square正在加速布局元宇宙和[加密货币](https://www.bitcoin86.com/)业务。上个月，SK Square宣布向韩国第四大加密交易所Korbit投资900亿韩元(约合7600万美元)，获得其35%的股份。 虽然Korbit在韩国市场的份额只有0.3%，但SK Square认为这是一个以低估值进入加密领域的好方法。SK Square计划在Korbit上发行可以购买SK集团公司产品和服务的加密货币。\",\"timestamp\":1639372630,\"title\":\"SK集团常务董事：我们的业务需要向元宇宙发展\"},\"digest\":\"fiq0g757IkYzCsMQGliTgWTSu3k9blbpWbpMmIhe9eE\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x9D636f2d113B98314B39c85efD0532040602090b\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"z-OuqIOccWwB1itcynxaqhUonn7ofLcs_zUvBVA1OAY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"TfU7ErQZT4yHGkzGYlCeppWXRRI6OyasEHPo7HTympI\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"DR3EwT6ofhhG-d2MA61Q3OXB3vdx2QNLuk99cOFUNASEr2KHOnWGKpk--wKXi9Ht9DJwAuVLphCina5kCRvgAg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xc358a5287b392091211a5835f48c88a71e7846ed8933a73cf67d03c45aae3d271892a12f5dcb0faa960e0bbed482cb1711a0278226ae4c64a6eba8d1290e53611b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"z-OuqIOccWwB1itcynxaqhUonn7ofLcs_zUvBVA1OAY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"TfU7ErQZT4yHGkzGYlCeppWXRRI6OyasEHPo7HTympI\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"fiq0g757IkYzCsMQGliTgWTSu3k9blbpWbpMmIhe9eE\"}"